# xml-filter-through-union

## Description

Migrated to a declarative `.rra` rule with a precondition (RFC 0090 Phase 2).

## Rewrite

lhs: (filter ?pred (union ?all ?left ?right))
rhs: (union ?all (filter ?pred ?left) (filter ?pred ?right))
when: is_xml_function_filter("?pred")
